{"tid":1883582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"調查稱7成港人支持2047年後續實行一國兩制","createTime":"2020-02-17T05:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T05:54:06.000Z","uid":70063,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb8cbd44bcb4cdf4b39b007bae36789654975de","tid":1883582,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:08:22.000Z","msg":"民主思路的調查顯示，香港市民對一國兩制的評分下跌至3.53分。<br />\n<br />\n民主思路委託中大亞太研究所在去年6月、8月和12月，以隨機抽樣方式用電話訪問了一千名18歲以上的香港市民，以10分為滿分，發現市民對一國兩制的評分由4.58分下跌至3.53分。<br />\n<br />\n民主思路聯席召集人潘學智說，香港積壓了很多管治問題和深層次矛盾，在反修例運動下，市民憂慮被移交內地的公眾恐慌爆發，對於有關評分下跌，並不意外。<br />\n<br />\n潘學智又說，雖然不同派別的市民對一國兩制都有感到失望，但調查發現超過7成人仍然支持2047年後繼續實行一國兩制，包括自認本土派和自決派的市民。<br />\n<br />\n身份認同方面，調查發現由2018年12月至去年10月，市民對「香港人」的認同感由8.06分上升至8.41分，對「中國人」的身份認同感則由6.83分下跌至4.72分。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508989-20200217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508989-20200217.htm&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=4999bfc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1508989-20200217.htm&h=30f90a68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1508989-20200217.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n一國兩制害到港人雞毛鴨血，仲有7成人仍支持2047年後繼續實行一國兩制，香港人係咪傻撚咗？"},{"pid":"69f2132c67cc4e8e30c55360f7e1ebaa99e18870","tid":1883582,"uid":21139,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"民主思路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0aceb25a03988a59d3a89b5aa5503bd83ad6415","tid":1883582,"uid":254183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:09:28.000Z","msg":"因為港人腦中仲未有港獨的選項<br />\n只有一國兩制or一國一制"},{"pid":"7175fa75106a5c33cf27a267d894beb992e28a0b","tid":1883582,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"但調查發現超過7成人仍然支持2047年後繼續實行一國兩制，包括自認本土派和自決派的市民<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d72b0640754c21ba02066dbe9d7ffcef33a224d","tid":1883582,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:10:51.000Z","msg":"中間派喺香港冇市場㗎,收皮啦."},{"pid":"9c4e7f7803bf832322791cfc432f1f419b9c2203","tid":1883582,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:11:46.000Z","msg":"未執咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583a733e96fe9ddb94145062e0ccb8f575ae51f7","tid":1883582,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"好過冇"},{"pid":"90450ca54b8ea47e0ad1c9912ffbc669d41f4477","tid":1883582,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"七成人支持又點？<br />\n<br />\n事實係一個人話事"},{"pid":"f3ceef2882c652efe1d284a1d04b499ab313a8b2","tid":1883582,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"收皮，行左20年仲唔夠慘啊<br />\n仲行多幾十年，真係移民算"},{"pid":"0acaf1e86078eef57b75c7ccd1776740527cd8c4","tid":1883582,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:14:03.000Z","msg":"即係3 成港獨"},{"pid":"0f6a64b3fca149eb1a4c64acb3ebd74b0a62151f","tid":1883582,"uid":304361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"一國兩制 本身唔同人定義已經唔同, 咁樣問根本無意思。"},{"pid":"469d084515cea9851fae7437867a4f85fc0b42ca","tid":1883582,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:14:45.000Z","msg":"民主私露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c208fc84079045cc2b73cf3bdc5a68194e2791a","tid":1883582,"uid":64953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:14:45.000Z","msg":"我打算組返個民主菲利<br />\n有冇人John"},{"pid":"183332e7dfec5644f9dacfd3efbff0acb1bafdb2","tid":1883582,"uid":263349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:16:31.000Z","msg":"下 咩民調? 可信？<br />\n<br />\n仲要永續一國兩制 嫌呢廿年仲未受夠？"},{"pid":"4282c69c3b7553a1fc5dfc772eefbd7742c1c570","tid":1883582,"uid":268537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0aceb25a03988a59d3a89b5aa5503bd83ad6415","tid":1883582,"uid":254183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:09:28.000Z","msg":"因為港人腦中仲未有港獨的選項<br />\n只有一國兩制or一國一制"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:17:28.000Z","msg":"明顯只提供兩個選項啦<br />\n邊個組織會公開支持港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3898c475f05c45c25071e93cb89dc700ee328249","tid":1883582,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"2019就實行左啦  未宣布姐"},{"pid":"2060c59f876ff13d83690bd43afb46bf85fe33ea","tid":1883582,"uid":310883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"民主思路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7少陣啦樓豬"},{"pid":"522522ab1a901537c63ff29f7ef492b026d3e65f","tid":1883582,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"支持一國兩制就唔係本土派啦"},{"pid":"45074c1ebecdc0bec969ee7f7f5ff5dcae95cdb9","tid":1883582,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4ee1b1cb7e7891c45840d62fe2462b86602bc4","tid":1883582,"uid":123926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:23:31.000Z","msg":"Google 民主思路:<br />\n<br />\n2015年成立的議政組織民主思路，當年由退出公民黨的湯家驊牽頭成立。近日逃犯條例修訂爭議之際，多名聯席召集人於陸續退出，最後一位的中大亞太研究所經濟研究中心副主任宋恩榮，今日也宣佈求去。他形容，民主思路正不斷從政治光譜中間的溫和民主定位，移向建制的一端。"},{"pid":"e91eb3072ca79dae5695c2d8a8ec1f8d97fd2b05","tid":1883582,"uid":203867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"